Final Submission Statement
This resubmission addresses the feedback provided regarding completeness, usability, and feature accessibility.
A dedicated home page (/) has been added as the application’s entry point. The home page clearly explains the purpose of the eCommerce application and allows users to browse products or access authentication features without requiring prior knowledge of URL paths. Non‑authentication functionality (product browsing) is now visible and accessible directly from the home page, ensuring authentication is no longer the primary focus or barrier to discovery.
Login, registration, logout, and forgotten password functionality are implemented using Django’s authentication system and exposed through browser‑accessible navigation. The product catalogue is reachable through clear links, and users can navigate the application entirely via the interface rather than manually entering routes.
Supporting screenshots demonstrating browser navigation, product access before login, and authentication flows have been added to the project for clarity. Project structure and application separation have been maintained to reflect good code organization practices.
